{"tid":244710,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇中華聯邦主義","createTime":"2017-05-15T15:39:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T11:55:09.000Z","uid":116429,"like":6,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ba0ca5d8d4506a748ce8c47471efb8c7fbb5b356","tid":244710,"uid":116429,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T15:39:03.000Z","msg":"泛指近代以來主張中國、台灣、香港、澳門甚至漢字文化圈實行聯邦制嘅思想，提出地方政權應有自治權利，改變一向以來華人普遍相信「大一統」嘅觀念，反對「中央集權」嘅制度，認為每個地區可以因應本地嘅差異，實施唔同嘅法律同政策，變成一個近似美國嘅聯邦國家，又或者係類似歐盟，由好多獨立國家組成嘅邦聯同盟。<br />\n<br />\n支持&mdash;&mdash;正評<br />\n反對&mdash;&mdash;負評<br />\n<br />\n參考：<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/中華聯邦主義\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E4%B8%AD%E8%8F%AF%E8%81%AF%E9%82%A6%E4%B8%BB%E7%BE%A9&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=7538d896\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/中華聯邦主義</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-yue.wikipedia.org/wiki/中華聯邦主義\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-yue.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E4%B8%AD%E8%8F%AF%E8%81%AF%E9%82%A6%E4%B8%BB%E7%BE%A9&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=37d7245d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh-yue.wikipedia.org/wiki/中華聯邦主義</a>"},{"pid":"e745a11b4c91ac1baafa4113689bfcbdd6a3faf9","tid":244710,"uid":116429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T15:41:20.000Z","msg":"想知反對者反對嘅原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba0c2922b70455e5f667faa7e6cfb2c4550e8e34","tid":244710,"uid":67824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T15:42:28.000Z","msg":"幾理想，不過無咩機會做到"},{"pid":"d0c2d201cad23775791e11642664549e29025805","tid":244710,"uid":67824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T15:43:00.000Z","msg":"唔反對，不過唔樂觀"},{"pid":"def27b17ad7c14b19b393620f3e175c952a80a73","tid":244710,"uid":82142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T